---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">About Brian</h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Born with a deep love for music, Brian's journey began at age 4 in Portugal, learning piano, guitar, and drums. When he moved to the U.S. at
          11, he discovered the vibrant world of American music and found his calling as a DJ.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          His multicultural upbringing gives him a unique edge. Seamlessly blending everything from Portuguese classics and Latin rhythms to Hip-Hop,
          House, and timeless oldies. Whether it's a song from 50 years ago or released just hours before your event, Brian knows how to pack the
          dance floor.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          As a bilingual professional who studies electronics and acoustics, Brian combines technical expertise with an innate ability to read the
          crowd and create unforgettable moments through music.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">20+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Years Experience</div>
          </div>

          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@DJBrianRodrigues"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer group"
          >
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              350K+
            </div>
            <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">YouTube Views</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-3xl">
          <Image src={brianImage} alt="DJ Brian Rodrigues" class="w-full h-80 object-cover object-top rounded-2xl mb-6" width={400} height={320} />

          <blockquote class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 italic leading-relaxed">
            "Music is the universal language that brings people together. From the moment I step behind the decks, my goal is simple: to create those
            magical moments where everyone feels the beat and dances like nobody's watching."
          </blockquote>
          <cite class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-semibold mt-4 block">- Brian Rodrigues</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Event Types Section */}
    <div class="mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Event Specialties</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Creating magical moments for every celebration, from intimate gatherings to grand festivities
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-16">
        {
          eventTypes.map((event, index) => (
            <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-6 text-center transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-2">
              <div class={`absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br ${event.color} opacity-90 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300`} />
              <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-3">{event.icon}</div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm md:text-base leading-tight">{event.name}</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300" />
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      {/* Cultural Specialties */}
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h4 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Cultural Music Expertise</h4>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Bridging cultures through music with authentic sounds from around the world
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {
          culturalSpecialties.map((culture, index) => (
            <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-3">{culture.flag}</div>
              <h5 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">{culture.name}</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">{culture.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
